    <text>
    <body>
        <p>Louisville, Kentucky, pension agent. Kentucky native. Married to Cara Barkley. Father of R. B. Barkley, Mary Barkley, Elizabeth Barkley, Fannie Barkley, John C. Barkley, and Joseph F. Barkley. Pension agent and notary public in Louisville in 1860.</p>

    </body>
